title: Screenshot from 2016-10-24 15-37-15.png
description:
Big update for budgie-remix 16.04 users!

• Latest Pocillo icon theme
• Brand new Budgie Desktop version v10.2.8
• Updated version of budgie-screenshot-applet
• Same packages as 16.10 "Yakkety" now
• Much more maintenance updates and bug fixes

sudo apt update
sudo apt full-upgrade

If you are using Plank and Arc theme, open Plank Preferences and choose the GTK+ theme. Recommended icon size is 32px.

Look out for the Places and IBUS applets new in Budgie Desktop v10.2.8﻿
comments.comment: +Cyber Joe - that is a weather app called gis-weather (http://www.noobslab.com/2015/04/gis-weather-widget-updated-and-now.html). Not sure about my-weather-indicator - if it is an appindicator based widget then with the upcoming appindicator support it should be displayed ok. Will try to remember to test with my-weather-indicator.
